sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / KServe Gateway
    participant API as vllm-cpu API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Auth as Auth Middleware<br/>(optional API key)
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine<br/>CPU Backend (v1)
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(PVC / S3)
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 1: Model Inference Request

    Client->>API: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer API key (optional)
    API->>Auth: Validate API key<br/>(if --api-key set)
    Auth-->>API: Authorized

    API->>Engine: Inference request
    Engine->>Storage: Read model weights<br/>(local filesystem / mounted PVC)
    Storage-->>Engine: Model tensors (cached)

    Note right of Engine: CPU inference via<br/>PyTorch + C++ kernels<br/>(IPEX on x86_64)

    Engine-->>API: Prediction result
    API-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>(streaming SSE or batch)

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 2: Model Download (Online Mode)

    Note right of Engine: Only when HF_HUB_OFFLINE=0<br/>(default in Konflux image)

    Engine->>HF: GET model files<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: HF_TOKEN (Bearer)
    HF-->>Engine: Model artifacts<br/>(weights, tokenizer, config)
    Engine->>Storage: Cache model locally

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Scrape

    participant Prom as Prometheus Scraper

    Prom->>API: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP 8000/TCP<br/>No auth required
    API-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics<br/>(latency, throughput, queue)

    Note over Client,HF: Flow 4: gRPC Inference (Optional)

    participant GRPC as vllm-cpu gRPC<br/>50051/TCP HTTP/2

    Client->>GRPC: gRPC inference request<br/>50051/TCP<br/>No TLS (insecure port)
    GRPC->>Engine: Inference request
    Engine-->>GRPC: Prediction result
    GRPC-->>Client: gRPC response
